提起上訴狀(須附繕本)。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　6 　　月　　24　　日\r\n                          書記官  張清秀","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PDEV/111%2c%e6%96%97%e5%b0%8f%2c178%2c20220624%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PDEV,111,斗小,178,20220624,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"斗小","JNO":"178","JDATE":"20220624","JTITLE":"清償債務"}